name: Buy a Lot of Things
overview: BuyaLotofThings.com is a wholesale company located in New York. They service thousands of retailers nationwide. BuyaLotofThings.com is the premiere online wholesaler and closeout company that helps small businesses to compete against larger enterprises by offering hundreds of high-quality goods at prices close to those at which large chains purchase. Minimum order is only a case of any product giving small businesses the opportunity to quickly turn merchandise rather than having the dollars tied up in inventory. They help small stores compete with big chains on both selection and price. BuyaLotofThings.com is the supplier for wholesale and resell for Ebay, Retail Stores, Flea Markets and your community.
